    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but why does the machine have to keep running if there's no life in it anymore? it feels so heavy and pointless. if the person who made the art is gone, then the body is just... a burden. a cage for something that doesn't exist. it feels like i'm just wasting space and resources for a creature that isn't even alive. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just let the machine stop?",
